{"id":2468,"date":"2024-12-07T13:01:07","date_gmt":"2024-12-07T13:01:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/guwahatielectrocare.com\/?page_id=2468"},"modified":"2024-12-07T13:07:29","modified_gmt":"2024-12-07T13:07:29","slug":"refund-policy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/guwahatielectrocare.com\/refund-policy\/","title":{"rendered":"Refund Policy"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"2468\" class=\"elementor elementor-2468\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2bf38e9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2bf38e9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8df6766 elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8df6766\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Refund Policy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9681753 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9681753\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20b9af8 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"20b9af8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Refund Policy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1dc2375 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1dc2375\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At Guwahati Electro Care, customer satisfaction is our priority. We strive to deliver exceptional repair services for your home appliances. However, if you are not entirely satisfied with our service, we have a transparent and fair refund policy to address your concerns.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67d0480 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"67d0480\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col relative items-end\">\n<div class=\"pt-0\">\n<div class=\"gizmo-shadow-stroke flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full\">\n<div class=\"h-full w-full\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.5em;\">1. Eligibility for Refund<\/strong><\/div><div class=\"h-full w-full\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);\">You may be eligible for a refund under the following circumstances:<\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"group\/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\"><div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\"><div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\"><div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"0719d23d-fbd0-43a2-9f21-d91efe88c36b\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\n<ul>\n<li>The service was not performed as agreed upon or described.<\/li>\n<li>The appliance remains non-functional due to negligence on our part.<\/li>\n<li>The parts replaced are found to be defective and were under warranty.<\/li>\n<li>Cancellation of service prior to commencement.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>2. Non-Refundable Cases<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Refunds will not be provided in the following instances:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Issues arise due to customer negligence, misuse, or improper handling of the appliance after the repair.<\/li>\n<li>The repair service is fully completed, and the appliance is in working condition as agreed upon.<\/li>\n<li>Delays caused by factors beyond our control, such as unavailability of parts.<\/li>\n<li>If the customer refuses to allow our technicians to verify or resolve the reported issue.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>3. Process for Requesting a Refund<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>If you are eligible for a refund, follow these steps to submit your request:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Contact Us:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Email:<\/strong> <a rel=\"noopener\">electrocareguwahati@gmail.com<\/a><\/li>\n<li><strong>Phone:<\/strong> 8471993952<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Provide the following details:\n<ul>\n<li>Service invoice number.<\/li>\n<li>A detailed explanation of the issue.<\/li>\n<li>Any relevant documentation or evidence (e.g., photos or videos of the appliance issue).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Our team will review your request and respond within <strong>7 business days<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>4. Refund Resolution<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Once your refund request is approved, we will process the refund using the same payment method you used for the transaction. Please note:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Refunds may take <strong>5\u201310 business days<\/strong> to reflect in your account.<\/li>\n<li>For cash payments, refunds will be issued in cash or bank transfer, as per mutual agreement.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>5. Service Cancellation Policy<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>If you wish to cancel a scheduled service:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Before Technician Arrival:<\/strong> No cancellation fees will apply, and a full refund will be processed.<\/li>\n<li><strong>After Technician Arrival:<\/strong> A nominal fee for technician visit and diagnosis may be deducted from the refund amount.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>6. Replacement Parts Warranty<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Any parts replaced during the service are covered under the manufacturer\u2019s warranty policy. If a part is found to be defective within the warranty period:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>We will replace the part free of charge.<\/li>\n<li>Refunds for parts will only be provided if a replacement is unavailable.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>7. Contact Us for Refund Queries<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding our refund policy, feel free to contact us:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Email:<\/strong> <a rel=\"noopener\">electrocareguwahati@gmail.com<\/a><\/li>\n<li><strong>Phone:<\/strong> 8471993952<\/li>\n<li><strong>Address:<\/strong> Sankardev Nagar Path, Near DC Guest House, Housing Colony, Swaraj Nagar, Ganeshguri, Guwahati, Assam 781006<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Refund Policy Refund Policy At Guwahati Electro Care, customer satisfaction is our priority. We strive to deliver exceptional repair services [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sid